OL,6,FA woman has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder after she stabbed a man to
OL,8,Fdeath outside a pub in Maidstone.
OL,10,FStephanie Langley killed Matthew
OL,11,FBryant, 52, during an unprovoked
OL,12,Fattack at around 6pm on Monday 11
OL,13,FSeptember 2023.
OL,15,FMaidstone Crown Court heard how just
OL,16,F20 minutes before the fatal attack,
OL,17,FLangley had driven to the Hare and
OL,18,FHounds public house and argued with Mr
OL,19,FBryant.
