OL,6,FLangley drove to Maidstone East train
OL,7,Fstation and removed a large kitchen
OL,8,Fknife from her car before returning to
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FWatch: The 999 call made by Matthew
OL,12,FBryant.
OL,14,FWhen she returned to the pub, Matthew
OL,15,Fwas on the phone to 999 operators
OL,16,Freporting the earlier argument, and it
OL,17,Fwas then she approached him and
OL,18,Fknocked his mobile to the floor.
