OL,6,FThe victim turned and bent down to
OL,7,Fretrieve his phone and, as he stood
OL,8,Fup, Langley stabbed him in the back
OL,9,Ftwice. She then struck a fatal blow to
OL,10,Fhis chest.
OL,12,FKent Police officers arrested her at
OL,13,Fthe scene a short while afterwards.
OL,15,FTwo days later, Langley, of Wilsons
OL,16,FLane, East Farleigh, was charged with
OL,17,Fmurder and possessing a knife in a
OL,18,Fpublic place.
OL,20,FWatch: Langley is arrested.
