OL,6,FThe 54-year-old denied murdering Mr
OL,7,FBryant, but pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fpossessing an offensive weapon. She
OL,9,Fwas convicted of the murder on
OL,10,FWednesday, 1 May 2024, following a
OL,11,Ftrial at Maidstone Crown Court.
OL,13,FLangley remains remanded in custody
OL,14,Fand a date for sentencing at the same
OL,15,Fcourt will be fixed on 7 May.
OL,17,FDetective Constable Hannah Crittenden,
OL,18,Fof the Kent and Essex Serious Crime
OL,19,FDirectorate, said:
